OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FA British crew member requires urgent
OL,8,Fmedical care and a passenger from the
OL,9,FUK remains in a critical but stable
OL,10,Fcondition following a suspected
OL,11,Fhantavirus outbreak on a cruise ship
OL,12,Fin the Atlantic Ocean.
OL,14,FThree people have died and two cases
OL,15,Fof the virus have been confirmed, tour
OL,16,Foperator Oceanwide Expeditions said.
OL,18,FThe confirmed cases include a British
OL,19,Fpassenger receiving care in South
OL,20,FAfrica and a Dutch woman who passed
OL,21,Faway on April 27 after disembarking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
