OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe company said in a statement on
OL,8,FMonday that two staff members ` one
OL,9,FBritish and one Dutch ` were
OL,10,Fcontinuing to show "acute respiratory
OL,11,Fsymptoms", one mild and one severe.
OL,13,FThe suspected outbreak was reported on
OL,14,Fthe Dutch-flagged cruise ship MV
OL,15,FHondius, which was sailing from
OL,16,FArgentina to Cape Verde.
OL,26,@rD@TOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
