FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FOceanwide Expeditions confirmed the
OL,8,FBritish tourist remains in a "critical
OL,9,Fbut stable" condition after being
OL,10,Fmedically evacuated to South Africa on
OL,11,FApril 27, where they are being treated
OL,12,Fin an intensive care unit in
OL,13,FJohannesburg.
OL,15,FThe ship's journey began on April 1,
OL,16,Fand a passenger died on board on April
OL,17,F11, Oceanwide Expeditions said.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
