PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe cause of death could not be
OL,8,Fdetermined on board. On April 24, this
OL,9,Fpassenger was disembarked on St
OL,10,FHelena, with his wife accompanying the
OL,11,Frepatriation.
OL,13,FThe wife became unwell during the
OL,14,Freturn journey and died. Authorities
OL,15,Flater confirmed she tested positive
OL,16,Ffor a variant of hantavirus.
OL,18,FBoth passengers were Dutch nationals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
