FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FOn May 2, a German passenger on board
OL,8,Fdied. The cause has not yet been
OL,9,Festablished, the tour operator
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FThe company added that guests will not
OL,13,Fbe disembarking in Cape Verde, except
OL,14,Ffor three individuals who will be
OL,15,Fmedically evacuated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
