PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"Dutch authorities are actively
OL,8,Fpreparing a medical evacuation of the
OL,9,Ftwo symptomatic individuals along with
OL,10,Fthe individual associated with the
OL,11,Fguest that passed away," a company
OL,12,Fstatement said.
OL,14,F"This will involve two specialised
OL,15,Faircraft equipped with the necessary
OL,16,Fmedical equipment and staffed by
OL,17,Ftrained medical crews.
OL,19,F"This is not confirmed and is subject
OL,20,Fto change."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]vD@AOU{D@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
