PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe ship may instead continue to Las
OL,8,FPalmas or Tenerife, but no final
OL,9,Fdisembarkation point has been
OL,10,Ffinalised.
OL,12,FHantavirus infections, which are
OL,13,Fusually spread by infected rodents'
OL,14,Furine or faeces, can lead to severe
OL,15,Frespiratory illness and can sometimes
OL,16,Fbe fatal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
