PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"This is a deeply worrying time for
OL,9,Fall those on board the MV Hondius and
OL,10,Fthe families of those affected by the
OL,11,Fhantavirus outbreak.
OL,13,F"FCDO (Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,14,FDevelopment Office) Consular teams
OL,15,Fhave been stood up across the UK,
OL,16,FSouth Africa, Spain and Portugal to
OL,17,Fsupport British nationals and we are
OL,18,Fworking around the clock with our
OL,19,Finternational partners, including the
OL,20,Fcruise ship operator.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
