OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778033004
OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"FCDO teams are also in contact with
OL,8,Fthe family of a British man who was a
OL,9,Fpassenger on the ship and is now in
OL,10,Fhospital in South Africa."
OL,12,FThe risk to the wider public remains
OL,13,Flow, according to Hans Henri P Kluge,
OL,14,Fthe WHO regional director for Europe.
OL,15,FHe added that there is "no need for
OL,16,Fpanic or travel restrictions".
OL,18,FWhile it is rare, hantavirus
OL,19,Finfections can spread between people,
OL,20,Faccording to the WHO.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@ZO]wD@XOUxD@]O]
