OL,3,CBritish crew member needs 'urgent'
OL,4,Ccare after suspected hantavirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThere is no specific treatment or
OL,8,Fcure, but patients have a better
OL,9,Fchance of survival if they receive
OL,10,Fmedical attention early.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
